comments.body:
If you just made some effort, you could look into the stack trace and see were the problem appears:

https://github.com/appcelerator/titanium_mobile/blob/master/iphone/Classes/TiUITabProxy.m#L96-97

You are obviously looking for a window, but it isn’t a TiWindowProxy for some reason.
That’s obviously a bug in Titanium, I think.
Resolving this ticket as a duplicate of TC-3613. Please do not file duplicate tickets even if you disagree with the comments posted in the original ticket.
